comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T22:00:59.149Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-13: exhaustive all-status search found the broad beyond-PM story pm-8ngt and VCS exemplar pm-xtrd but no digital-twin exemplar; this is phase 2 beneath that canonical lineage and depends on public graph primitives."
  "2026-07-22T18:26:41.278Z",codex-root,"Relationship rationale: the digital-twin exemplar must prove temporal replay and graph behavior under scale, conformance, and policy constraints, not merely demonstrate a domain schema. The roadmap-policy link keeps it exploratory until promotion evidence exists."
  "2026-07-23T10:13:41.158Z",codex-root,"Implementation start 2026-07-23: building the bounded production-facility digital-twin exemplar as a first-party package using public @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk exports only. Scope covers temporal entity and relationship events, point-in-time replay, invariants, conflicts/corrections, schema evolution, federation/import-export, tests, docs, and packed-consumer proof. All-status duplicate check reused pm-kr3t beneath pm-8ngt; no new item created."
  "2026-07-23T11:18:49.753Z",codex-root,"Evidence: a freshly rebuilt global pm binary initialized an isolated temporary workspace, installed digital-twin, created facility/machine/utility entities with normalized pm-* IDs, added a utility dependency, reconstructed machine state at event time, surfaced utility_not_running, idempotently re-imported four events as skips, and verified a valid checkpoint with a 3-node/1-edge graph. The temporary workspace was moved to trash after verification."
  "2026-07-23T11:19:15.165Z",codex-root,"Evidence correction: the temporary filesystem does not support trash. After the successful proof, the exact isolated path /tmp/tmp.yG3Q12ZmSw was verified and deleted directly; it contained only this run's disposable tracker and global extension state."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T11:19:15.794Z",codex-root,"The installed-package failure found during full-suite TDD was architectural: value imports from @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk cannot resolve after a bundled extension is copied into an otherwise empty tracker. The durable fix was to expand host-injected ExtensionCommandSdk services and keep package runtime SDK imports type-only."
